title: 139: QBs, pass rushers and Chargers GM Tom Telesco
itunes:title: 139: QBs, pass rushers and Chargers GM Tom Telesco
description:
Former NFL scouts Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks discuss QBs, rushing the passer and recap the Week 12 NFL action. San Diego Chargers general manager Tom Telesco joins the show and gives his insight into the football operations world. DJ and Bucky also break down what to expect during Bowl Season in college football.
